@startuml
' Meritum — Diagrama UML de Comunicação
' Cenário: UC05 - Professor envia moedas para aluno.
' Fontes: README.md; coin.routes.ts; coin-service.ts; moedaService.ts; schema.prisma.

!pragma layout smetana

title Meritum — Diagrama UML de Comunicação — UC05 Enviar Moedas

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam maxMessageSize 40
skinparam object {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #111827
}

top to bottom direction

object "professor:\nProfessor" as Professor
object "page:\nEnviarMoedasPage" as Page
object "apiClient:\nHTTP client" as ApiClient
object "action:\nCoinRoutes" as Action
object "guard:\nJWT + RBAC" as Guard
object "service:\nCoinService" as CoinService
object "persistence:\nPrisma repositories\n+ UnitOfWork" as Persistence
object "db:\nPostgreSQL meritum" as DB <<database>>
object "eventBus:\nDomain Events" as EventBus
object "email:\nEmailService" as Email
object "smtp:\nSMTP/Ethereal" as SMTP

Professor -right- Page : 1. preencher envio
Page -right- ApiClient : 2. enviarMoedas(input)
ApiClient -right- Action : 2.1 POST + JWT
Action -down- Guard : 2.2 autenticar\n+ role professor
Guard -right- CoinService : 3. enviarMoedas(dto)

CoinService -down- Persistence : 3.1 buscar professor\ne aluno
Persistence -down- DB : 3.2 SELECT users,\nprofessors, students
CoinService -right- CoinService : 3.3 validar regras\nde domínio

CoinService -down- Persistence : 4. transação Prisma\ndeduzir, creditar, registrar
Persistence -down- DB : 4.1 UPDATE/INSERT\nCOMMIT

CoinService -right- EventBus : 5. publicar evento
EventBus -down- Email : 5.1 notificar aluno
Email -down- SMTP : 5.2 enviar e-mail

CoinService -up- Action : 6. transação criada
Action -up- ApiClient : 6.1 201 JSON
ApiClient -up- Page : 6.2 retorno
Page -up- Professor : 7. confirmação

note bottom of CoinService
  Comunicação de um cenário. Não representa todos os módulos.
  A persistência agrupa ProfessorBalancePort, StudentBalancePort,
  TransactionRepository e UnitOfWork observados no código.
end note

@enduml
